snippet.title: Audio file of Johnny Depp revealing that Amber Heard throws pots at him
snippet.description:
At today's High Court hearing, Amber Heard and two of her friends were accused of 'putting their heads together' to lie about claims that Depp attacked her and also smashed up the their Los Angeles penthouse in 2016. Police were called to the incident of 21 May 2016 with two officers testifying last week that they did not see Heard with any injuries or damage to the property.
